{"title":"云中网络","date":"2019-06-25T14:49:24.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2019年6月25日","L":"2019/06/25","MM-DD":"06-25"},"link":"2019/06/25/24. 云中网络","tags":["网络协议"],"categories":["网络协议"],"updated":"2019-12-01T14:56:46.090Z","content":"<!-- build time:Sun Aug 23 2020 20:59:40 GMT+0800 (GMT+08:00) --><h2 id=\"虚拟网卡的原理\">虚拟网卡的原理<a href=\"2019/06/25/24. 云中网络#虚拟网卡的原理\"></a></h2><p><img src=\"https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/9a/7e/9a257afaa9c8a158a5a99e2df00dcf7e.jpg\" alt=\"img\" class=\"article-img\"></p><h2 id=\"虚拟网卡连接到云中\">虚拟网卡连接到云中<a href=\"2019/06/25/24. 云中网络#虚拟网卡连接到云中\"></a></h2><ul><li><p>共享与互通</p><p><img src=\"https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/69/a1/6976194513a8ec9066c1dd26e7b07ca1.jpg\" alt=\"img\" class=\"article-img\"></p><p><img src=\"https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/93/f4/9347b67409e26924ea9358f052f2e9f4.jpg\" alt=\"img\" class=\"article-img\"></p><p><img src=\"https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/e5/07/e55e9a85106d9086e51cd649a182d707.jpg\" alt=\"img\" class=\"article-img\"></p><p><img src=\"https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/a8/c0/a859bb918ab4ca53c3542a6b18884ec0.jpg\" alt=\"img\" class=\"article-img\"></p><p><img src=\"https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/a1/b7/a145ea19a844b3e38834efbf0f4cedb7.jpg\" alt=\"img\" class=\"article-img\"></p><p><img src=\"https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/2d/c4/2dd447992fbf4901f92a3dfdf8086bc4.jpg\" alt=\"img\" class=\"article-img\"></p><p><img src=\"https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/72/8b/72b49cdeeb8846025f310a1f59b6b88b.jpg\" alt=\"img\" class=\"article-img\"></p><p><img src=\"https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/49/f3/499e17daa9495ccf9f9497a165cc50f3.jpg\" alt=\"img\" class=\"article-img\"></p></li><li><p>隔离</p><p><img src=\"https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/df/e0/dfc95f72325ab13c2f9551cfccc073e0.jpg\" alt=\"img\" class=\"article-img\"></p></li><li>灵活</li></ul><h2 id=\"小结\">小结<a href=\"2019/06/25/24. 云中网络#小结\"></a></h2><ul><li>云计算的关键技术是虚拟化，这里我们重点关注的是，虚拟网卡通过打开 TUN/TAP 字符设备的方式，将虚拟机内外连接起来</li><li>云中的网络重点关注四个方面，共享、隔离、互通、灵活。其中共享和互通有两种常用的方式，分别是桥接和 NAT，隔离可以通过 VLAN 的方式</li></ul><h2 id=\"思考\">思考<a href=\"2019/06/25/24. 云中网络#思考\"></a></h2><ul><li>为了直观，这一节的内容我们以桌面虚拟化系统举例。在数据中心里面，有一款著名的开源软件 OpenStack，这一节讲的网络连通方式对应 OpenStack 中的哪些模型呢？</li><li>这一节的最后，我们也提到了，本节提到的网络配置方式比较不灵活，你知道什么更加灵活的方式吗？</li></ul><!-- rebuild by neat -->","prev":{"title":"移动网络","link":"2019/06/25/23. 移动网络"},"next":{"title":"设计模式","link":"2019/06/05/设计模式"},"plink":"https://www.jayli.cn/2019/06/25/24. 云中网络/","toc":[{"title":"虚拟网卡的原理","id":"虚拟网卡的原理","index":"1"},{"title":"虚拟网卡连接到云中","id":"虚拟网卡连接到云中","index":"2"},{"title":"小结","id":"小结","index":"3"},{"title":"思考","id":"思考","index":"4"}],"copyright":{"link":"<a href=\"https://www.jayli.cn/2019/06/25/24. 云中网络/\" title=\"云中网络\">https://www.jayli.cn/2019/06/25/24. 云中网络/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","published":"2019年6月25日","author":"Jayli"}}